Accepted formats: JPEG, PNG    Resolution:    -   Square (Aspect ratio: 1: 1):    Optimal resolution: 1080 x 1080 px    Minimum resolution: 600x600    -   Vertical "Portrait" (Aspect ratio: 1: 1.25):    Optimal resolution: 1080 x 1350 px    Minimum resolution: 600x400    -   Horizontal "Landscape" (Aspect ratio: 1.91: 1):    Optimal resolution: 1080 x 566 px    Minimum resolution: 600 x 749      Gif:    Maximum 10 mb    Maximum resolution: 640 pixels    Formato accetato: GIF    Recommended platform: Giphy  Stakes: Rejected= 0 stake Sufficient = 1 stakes More than Enough = 2 stakes Good = 4 stakes Very Good = 6 stakes Extraordinary = 12 stakes  Spreadsheet link: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1OHMZE4eiGHrZLJFEFjY4vaRoGBS_fLuy-gJIxCyTuD8/edit?usp=sharing   ______________________________________________________________________     TRANSLATION & MODERATION 12% of total bounty pool  How to participate: In order to be admitted to this specific Bounty program, participant must first of all join at Followine Official Telegram Group and for each CONTENT created the participant must fill up this form: TRANSLATION & MODERATION FORM Selected candidates will receive an email response and will be invited to participate in a special group chat.  RULES: Reservation requests on bounty thread will be ignored. Every kind of work must first be approved by team. So please don't start working until we approve you.Unapproved translations/moderations will not be paid. Only for 1-2-3-4: Translations have to be original and professional, using translation tools like google translate leads to disqualification. Only for 1 e 5: A single dead thread/group will not be paid, it‚Äôs detrimental to the project. Translators/moderators must be responsible and moderate their threads/group while keeping them active. Publish news and updates regularly. Only for 1: Translators-moderators are applied to wear Followine signature and avatar and have to keep both signature and avatar until the end of the bounty campaign. Only for 4: participants will have to publish the translated articles their own blogging account (Medium, Steemit, Wordpress or others platforms) and then they will have to communicate the links to the Followine bounty managers.  Types of translations/moderations and relative stakes: 1 Official ANN and Bounty Thread translation and moderation. Reward= 80 stakes 2 Translation of Whitepaper. Reward= 300 stakes 3 Translation of Website. Reward= 120 stakes 4 Translation Followine post (official articles). Reward= 15 stakes 5 Creation and moderation of unofficial telegram group (min. 100 members)= 60 stakes  ______________________________________________________________________  <<< EXTRA BONUS ‚ÄúHard Work‚Äù: 30000 WINE >>>  The Followine project will assign an extra bonus to participants who show strong commitment. The bonus will be equally divided among participants who reach at least 1 of the following REQUIREMENTS:  Complete minimum 65% of at least one of the following campaigns: signature, facebook, twitter, linkedin. (5 weeks out of 7) Produce at least 2 "video creation" rated at least "Good" Produce at least 3 unique ‚Äúwritten content creation‚Äù (no duplicates) rated at least "Good". Produce at least 5 "graphics creation" rated at least " Good " Produce at least 3 "translation & moderation" activities  Note: if a participant reaches more than one requirement he will receive more WINE. For example: if he reaches 3 requirements he will get three times more WINE than those who reach only one  ______________________________________________________________________  Disclaimer To prevent fraud and theft, the wallet address provided during signup cannot be changed for any reason. We reserve the right to remove from any campaign user spamming, cheating or using multi-accounts. Negative trust are not allowed to join this campaign, negative trust received during the campaign will result in permanently banning from any campaign, all stakes will be deleted. We reserve the right to remove any user from any campaign if there is a suspect of their dishonesty: we will not give any explanation. Users may not be accepted in the campaign for any reasons. We reserve the right to change, modify, add or remove portions of these terms and conditions at any time without prior notice and you accept and agree to the changes. It is your responsibility to check these Terms periodically for changes. We reserve the right to change the final reward of the campaign if not a minimum number of participants is reached.
